title: Shanklys Best of 2007 August
description:
Another month, another mixtape. Previews from new and forthcoming album releases from Okkervil River, Iron & Wine, Rilo Kiley, the Stereophonics, Akron/Family iLiKETRAiNS and Beruit; new singles by Bruce Springsteen, Super Furry Animals, Hot Hot Heat, Sambassadeur, the Hives and Bearsuit; and plenty of the usual remixes, live tracks and cover versions as well. Just wait til you hear Scout Niblett\&#039;s duet with Will Oldham. 

Shankly - making music count!
